title: The Egg Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, British, English
description: Casual setting on the second floor, near Central and Lime St stations. Usually 1 or 2 vegan soups daily, 3 daily specials at least 1 vegan. Menu includes vegan spicy beanburger, salads, quiche, and more. Special menu Sunday afternoon (full vegan roast). Vegan items clearly marked on the menu.
